#WeAreWilliams #F1 #Formula1 #FOS

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Jenson Button on July 08, 2021 tagging @radfordmotors.

node.text:
@radfordmotors has acquired the John Player Special trademark in the US. 

We’re so excited to have acquired this trademark. John Player Special is, without question, one of the most iconic racing liveries ever to grace a Formula 1 car. 

For me, it conjures images of the ‘Golden era’ of Formula One racing, adorning cars driven by heroes such as Emerson Fittipaldi , Mario Andretti and Ayrton Senna. Legends that inspired me to want to become a racing driver. 

We can’t wait to show you where this livery is going to be used, but expect to see it appearing on Radford cars in the near future. The sort of cars which evoke the great racing pedigree that these liveries bring with them.

#radfordreturns #JPS
